'''馬克斯·巴金漢'''（英文：Marcus Buckingham）是一名作家、演講者及商業顧問。<ref name=USAT>{{cite web|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/2005-03-03-buckingham-usat_x.htm|title=Business bows to an unlikely oracle: British boy wonder|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|first=Del|last=Jones|date=3 March 2005|accessdate=11 February 2015|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315163637/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/2005-03-03-buckingham-usat_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>馬克斯·巴金漢致力於釋放人類的天賦能力，提高公司職員的績效並開創未來人們的工作方式。<ref>{{cite web |author1=WOBI ON HIGH PERFORMANCE TEAMS |title=The exclusive digital masterclass with Marcus Buckingham |url=https://www.wobi.com/online-events-apac/wobi-on-high-performance-teams-marcus-buckingham/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=cpc&utm_term=now%20discover%20your%20strengths%20book&&gclid=CjwKCAjwv_iEBhASEiwARoemvE7J6gdCfmiNDItQc_rtdI9OHHqzT7ndPGgUt3DK821Yr5-tS1JZwBoCskMQAvD_BwE&gclid=CjwKCAjwv_iEBhASEiwARoemvE7J6gdCfmiNDItQc_rtdI9OHHqzT7ndPGgUt3DK821Yr5-tS1JZwBoCskMQAvD_BwE&gclsrc=aw.ds |website=WOBI |accessdate=2021-05-14 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515103905/https://www.wobi.com/online-events-apac/wobi-on-high-performance-teams-marcus-buckingham/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=cpc&utm_term=now%20discover%20your%20strengths%20book&&gclid=CjwKCAjwv_iEBhASEiwARoemvE7J6gdCfmiNDItQc_rtdI9OHHqzT7ndPGgUt3DK821Yr5-tS1JZwBoCskMQAvD_BwE&gclid=CjwKCAjwv_iEBhASEiwARoemvE7J6gdCfmiNDItQc_rtdI9OHHqzT7ndPGgUt3DK821Yr5-tS1JZwBoCskMQAvD_BwE&gclsrc=aw.ds |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==學習生涯==
馬克斯·巴金漢曾就讀於埃奇格羅夫學校（一所位於英格蘭南部赫特福德郡阿爾登納姆村的男子預科私立學校）<ref name=ES>{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/playing-to-his-strengths-the-beverly-hills-brit-whos-a-selfhelp-god-6678564.html|title=Playing to his strengths, the Beverly Hills Brit who's a self-help god|work=[[London_Evening_Standard|London Evening Standard]]|first=Chris|last=Blackhurst|date=5 December 2007|accessdate=11 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211050416/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/playing-to-his-strengths-the-beverly-hills-brit-whos-a-selfhelp-god-6678564.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之後就讀於阿爾登納姆學校（一所寄宿制的男孩立私立學校），及在1987年畢業於[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]][[彭布羅克學院|彭布羅克學院]]，獲得了社會政治學學位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pem.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Pembroke-Gazette-2010lo.pdf|title=Pembroke College - Cambridge Society Annual Gazette - Issue 84, September 2010 (pg.126 - 1984 - Marcus Buckingham)|work=Pembroke College - Cambridge Society|date=September 2010|accessdate=11 February 2015|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234126/http://www.pem.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Pembroke-Gazette-2010lo.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=WEDDINGS;Ms. Rinzler, Mr. Buckingham|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1996/03/17/style/weddings-ms-rinzler-mr-buckingham.html|accessdate=24 May 2011|newspaper=New York Times|date=17 March 1996|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415004701/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/03/17/style/weddings-ms-rinzler-mr-buckingham.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
在[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]學習期間，著名的[[教育心理學|教育心理學]]教授[[當奴·克利夫頓|當奴·克利夫頓]]招募了馬克斯·巴金漢進入選擇研究公司。<ref name=galluphistory>{{cite web|title=Corporate History |url=http://www.gallup.com/corporate/1357/corporate-history.aspx#4 |accessdate=24 May 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100106230652/http://www.gallup.com/corporate/1357/Corporate-History.aspx |archivedate=6 January 2010 }}</ref>選擇研究公司於1988年收購了[[蓋洛普|蓋洛普]]國際研究教育中心，並以[[蓋洛普|蓋洛普]]為名。作為[[蓋洛普|蓋洛普]]國際研究教育中心的一部分，馬克斯·巴金漢也成為[[蓋洛普|蓋洛普]]國際研究教育中心的成員，並與[[庫特·科夫曼|庫特·科夫曼]]合著了《[[首先，打破成規|首先，打破成規]]──八萬名傑出經理人的共通特質》<ref>{{cite news|title=The New York Times Business Best Sellers|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1999/10/10/business/the-new-york-times-business-best-sellers.html|accessdate=24 May 2011|newspaper=New York Times|date=10 October 1999|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422052851/https://www.nytimes.com/1999/10/10/business/the-new-york-times-business-best-sellers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。馬克斯·巴金漢主持多項職場績效的研究，後來成為[[作家|作家]]、[[研究員|研究員]]以及[[演說家|演說家]]，每年對全球超過250萬名聽眾演說。

==主要理念==
馬克斯·巴金漢認為人們應該專注於發揮自己的天賦，而不用擔心自己的劣勢。 作為研究人員，馬克斯·巴金漢證明了培養員工的天賦優勢與公司成功之間的相關性。 馬克斯·巴金漢最近的研究著眼於人類的實際工作方式，他解開了工作評估如何影響績效的發現，發現管理人員常常會在不知不覺中產生偏見和無益的反饋。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://thinkers50.com/biographies/marcus-buckingham-2/ |website=THINKERS50 RANKED THINKER |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-05-14 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514081625/https://thinkers50.com/biographies/marcus-buckingham-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

